\begin_inset Formula $2\cfrac{1}{2}$
\end_inset

倍,或者说
\begin_inset Formula $10$
\end_inset

米与
\begin_inset Formula $4$
\end_inset

米的比是
\begin_inset Formula $5:2$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

